<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span><span>Skill Damage +35%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases attack skill damage by 35%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/154d2e637eaa966dfad5b6805cfc514f2.png"></span><span>Potent Curse Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to curses by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>cursed them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/85285afa2a77c2880c1c006d8d0d214c2.png"></span><span>Gauge Accelerator +40%</span></dt><dd><div>Speeds the rate the mode gauge decreases by 40%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div>Note: The Sacred Maiden skill will be upgraded when raised to Lv. 4, but the skill gauge will fill more slowly. Additionally, the skill gauge will fill even more slowly each time Skill Shift activates and changes the skill to Phase II and Phase III.</div><div><br></div><div>We will remove the text about resetting Skill Shift from the details of skills with the Skill Shift feature.</div><div>Note: This change only affects the descriptive text. The conditions for resetting Skill Shift will not change. For information about resetting Skill Shift, select Help, then select Special Effects and see the About Resetting section under Skill Shift.</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1592460000,update_time1592359613